OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGlastonbury: Sir Lenny     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHenry discusses festival   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdiversity                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Lenny Henry has said it is         
OL,6, "interesting" to see the apparent lack 
OL,7, of black people in the audience at     
OL,8, Glastonbury Festival.                  
OL,10,FThe actor and comedian, 63, said he was
OL,11,Falso "surprised" by the lack of diverse
OL,12,Ffaces at other UK festivals.           
OL,14,FHe made the comments while in          
OL,15,Fconversation with BBC journalist and   
OL,16,Fpresenter Clive Myrie for Radio Times. 
OL,18,FIt comes as the event's co-organiser,  
OL,19,FEmily Eavis, said Stormzy's performance
OL,20,Fin 2019 was "a little bit late".       
